Through simple trial-and-error, we find that the offset is +6. Just subtract 6 (with wraparound) from each letter, and you get the answer.

The problem was-
Znoy iovnkx ullkxy tkdz zu tu ykiaxoze. Tu cutjkx Igkygx cgy gyygyotgzkj. Znk lrgm oy {IXUYY_ZNK_XAHOIUT}

